## Appendix: Evidence Trail

This appendix catalogs the individual facts that inform the analysis above.
Each entry links back to its source material and records the extraction
confidence, verification status, and final assessed confidence.

All facts are listed in order of appearance within the investigation.
Confidence scores reflect the assessed reliability of each individual claim
based on source authority, corroboration, and extraction quality.

### Legend

| Field | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| Extraction Confidence | LLM confidence when extracting this fact from source text |
| Verification Status | Outcome of the verification loop (CONFIRMED, REFUTED, PENDING, UNVERIFIABLE) |
| Final Confidence | Combined credibility score after classification and verification |

